HEADWORD: Transmeate
<hw>Trans"me*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>transmeatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>transmeare</ets> to pass across;
<ets>trans</ets> across, over + <ets>meare</ets> to go.]</ety> <def>To
pass over or beyond.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
